token_lists.title: "CPP-IAM_Statics-_CLR" CRYSTALS
token_lists.description:
"CPP-IAM_Statics-02CLR_..." series is:

[COLOR Practice with Patterns] [Intermediate Algorithmic Multicomponent] [Statics]  Color version. Background color domination [slow color side] - Black. The "Main Crystal" is multicolored - splitted on two layers. The matrix is fragmented. The artwork connects intermediate cross-pattern`s instructions into Intermediate Algorithmic Multicomponent. The abstraction is dedicated to the "Metaball", "Voronoi diagram" and "Delaunay triangulation" transformations. The patterns are linked in specific way to draw the algorithmic abstraction. The energy of abstract processes in relationship of algorithms is linked inside. The pool of colors is filtered in custom way. JPG 2608*4096
